post_content:
HKUST Digital Images contains memories of early University events from 1988 to 1999. Supported by the Office of the Executive Vice-President and Provost, we have digitized images from slides, prints or negatives transferred to the University Archives from various offices, including Public Affairs Office and Publishing Technology Center (PTC). For photos of current University events please refer to the Photo Gallery of PTC. We encourage all members of the HKUST community and alumni to tag the images and provide more information about the events. Keep checking and share with your friends.

Contact Us

University Archives, HKUST Library Telephone: (852) 2358-6784 Email: lbarsc@ust.hk Location

HKUST Digital Images contains memories of early University events from 1988 to 1999. Supported by the Office of the Executive Vice-President and Provost, we have digitized images from slides, prints or negatives transferred to the University Archives from various offices, including Public Affairs Office and Publishing Technology Center (PTC). For photos of current University events please refer to the Photo Gallery of PTC. We encourage all members of the HKUST community and alumni to tag the images and provide more information about the events. Keep checking and share with your friends.
